<div class="content-group1">
  <span class="color1">
    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562802863/TEST_qdyrfq.png" alt="">
    <div class="flex-left">
      <h3 class="">Beat Procrastination and Achieve Your Goals!</h3>
      <div class="paragraph-height">
      <p class="paragraph-margin">Being productive can sometimes be a daunting task. But it doesn't have to be. With Conquered Time, you can find clarity and enjoy the process of self-improvement.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</span>

<div class="content-group2">
  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562763241/wejirjwejierw_xi1uxl.png" alt="">
  <div class="flex-right">
    <h3 class="">Step 1: Create A Tactical Journal</h3>
    <div class="paragraph-height">
    <p class="paragraph-margin">We usually procrastinate when our goals are too big or difficult to achive. So you first need to break down your large goals into small and managable milestones.</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-group3">
  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562763527/epepepepe_am8n9g.png" alt="">
  <div class="flex-left">
    <h3>Step 2: Begin Your Focus Timer</h3>
    <div class="paragraph-height">
    <p class=" paragraph-margin">Once you've made your tactical journal, you'll select any one of your chosen milestone and initiate your focus timer. During this timer you'll stay away from all distractions and work with complete dedication and present moment mindfulness.</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-group4">
  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562766176/woerkoeworwer_ivkkri.png" alt="">
  <div class="flex-right">
    <h3>Step 3: Refelect & Repeat</h3>
    <div class="paragraph-height">
    <p class="paragraph-margin"> You've escaped the limbo of procrastination and you've progressed one step closer to your goal, that's awesome! Now contemplate on the work you've done so far, take a samll break if you need it and then repeat the cycle.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-group5">
<div class="flex-main">
  <div class="banner-main">
    <h2 class="title-margin">Step 4: Realize Your True Potential</h2>
    <img class="img-artwork vert-move " src="https://res.cloudinary.com/doem0zjpf/image/upload/v1562638680/group_3x_jvunnq.png" alt="">
  </div>


  <form action="/journals" method="post">
    <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token %>
    <label class="hidden" for="title">Title:
    </label>
    <input class="form-textfield" type="text" placeholder="" name="journal[title]" id="title">

    <input class="form-submit" value="Begin Your Journey" type="submit">
  </form>
  </div>
